(156, 1, '2012-05-22 03:28:15', '2012-05-22 03:28:15', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Custom Web Design: Our team consists of some of the most talented and creative web designers out there. Our methods are guaranteed to improve your image and get people to take notice. We always strive to be innovators, and that’s why you do not have to worry about your website being drab or mundane. Whatever you can imagine, we can design. It’s that simple with Fitness Website Gurus.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Templates: No matter what website style you require, we can craft a basic, conversion-oriented template and take it from there. So don’t hesitate, get in touch with us today and see how we can assist you with all of  your website needs.</li>\r\n	<li>Web Development: Design is important, but without a strong backbone, it’s merely eye candy. Web development is that backbone. From widgets to flash integration, our goal is to make things functional and reliable so that your website’s visitors are happy. A poorly developed webpage just smacks of unprofessionalism, and that’s the last thing you want. Our staff has extensive experience and has worked on countless projects, as our testimonials attest to. With us, you’re in good hands.</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>E-commerce solutions</li>\r\n	<li>Customer reviews/testimonials</li>\r\n	<li>Customer opt-in measures</li>\r\n	<li>Widgets</li>\r\n	<li>Flash integration</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n	<li>Marketing: We want to get your name out there by establishing your brand and vastly increasing your company’s web presence.  To do so, we use effective techniques such as advanced search engine optimization (SEO), which will consistently generate hits to for website.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Services', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '7-revision-3', '', '', '2012-05-22 03:28:15', '2012-05-22 03:28:15', '', 7, 'http://fitnesswebsitegurus.com/7-revision-3/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
