(269, 1, '2012-08-01 16:12:00', '2012-08-01 16:12:00', '<strong>What is a mobile application?</strong>\r\nA mobile application is a program which has been developed for use on mobile devices. Applications, or apps, of all types exist, from pedometers to games.<br /><br />\r\n<strong>What platforms do you develop for?</strong>\r\nCurrently, we develop apps for all applicable Apple products.<br /><br />\r\n<strong>Why should I choose Fitness Website Gurus?</strong>\r\nWhen choosing Fitness Website Gurus, you know you are getting only top-quality service. Rest assured that your website/app is being developed by experienced professionals who know what they are doing. Your website/app will be completed promptly and for a fair price.<br /><br />\r\n<strong>Do I need a website?</strong>\r\nNowadays, it is absolutely imperative for any business to have a website. It is really the ultimate way to reach your customers and get the maximum amount of clients.<br /><br />\r\n<strong>Do I need a mobile website?</strong>\r\nIf you already have a website, it is crucial that you also get one that is optimized for mobile performance. Everywhere you look, someone is using an iPad, a smart phone, or some other mobile device, therefore it is important that your website detect when a visitor is using a mobile device and display a customized mobile version. The website will function better, and the user will be more satisfied; this is turn will lead to a higher conversion rate.<br /><br />\r\n<strong>What if I encounter problems with my app or website?</strong>\r\nIn the unlikely event that you are having problems with your app or your website, our support team is available online or via phone (during business hours) to answer your questions and resolve any issues.<br /><br />\r\n<strong>Does it matter that I do not live near you?</strong>\r\nOur work is primarily internet based, so whether you are local or international, our services are guaranteed to meet your needs. Also, you can email us at any time and we will respond promptly.<br /><br />\r\n<strong>Will I receive status updates regarding my project?</strong>\r\nYes. Clients can, upon request, regularly receive updates regarding the status of their product. We can also send drafts if needed. Our clients’ satisfaction is always our top priority.<br /><br />\r\n<strong>Upon completion of the job, can I still make changes?</strong>\r\nYes, adjustments can be made after the fact. Please contact us for further details.<br /><br />\r\n<strong>I have my own web hosting package, but would like a mobile website. Can I still use my existing package?</strong>\r\nYes, you can continue using your existing hosting provider.<br /><br />\r\n<strong>How much is an app going to cost me?</strong>\r\nWe offer competitive one-time app development fees. Fill out the form on our home page and get a free quote today!<br /><br />\r\n<strong>How much is a website going to cost me?</strong>\r\nWe offer multiple website packages to satisfy varying needs and budgets. Our Bronze package is priced at $39.99/mo, our Silver package is priced at $59.99/mo, and our Gold package is priced at $79.99/mo. There is a $99 start-up fee for all packages.', 'faq', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'faq', '', '', '2012-08-01 16:57:56', '2012-08-01 16:57:56', '', 0, 'http://fitnesswebsitegurus.com/?page_id=269', 0, 'page', '', 0),
