romptly.\r\n<strong>Will I receive status updates regarding my project?</strong>\r\nYes. Clients can, upon request, regularly receive updates regarding the status of their product. We can also send drafts if needed. Our clients’ satisfaction is always our top priority.\r\n<strong>Upon completion of the job, can I still make changes?</strong>\r\nYes, adjustments can be made after the fact. Please contact us for further details.\r\n<strong>I have my own web hosting package, but would like a mobile website. Can I still use my existing package?</strong>\r\nYes, you can continue using your existing hosting provider.\r\n<strong>How much is an app going to cost me?</strong>\r\nWe offer competitive one-time app development fees. Fill out the form on our home page and get a free quote today!\r\n<strong>How much is a website going to cost me?</strong>\r\nWe offer multiple website packages to satisfy varying needs and budgets. Our Bronze package is priced at $39.99/mo, our Silver package is priced at $59.99/mo, and our Gold package is priced at $79.99/mo. There is a $99 start-up fee for all packages.', 'faq', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '269-revision-9', '', '', '2012-08-01 16:57:20', '2012-08-01 16:57:20', '', 269, 'http://fitnesswebsitegurus.com/269-revision-9/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
